he roast. Allow the pork to rest for about 15 minutes before carving and serving.</p>', 'https://www.foodista.com/recipe/BVKG5VJM/apple-roasted-pork-loin', 'Foodista.com – The Cooking Encyclopedia Everyone Can Edit', 'pork loin
