Preheat the oven to 350 degrees Fahrenheit.

In a medium bowl, blend together 2 cups of flour, 1/2 cup sugar, and softened butter. Press into a 9" x 13" pan. Bake for 15 – 20 minutes or until the crust is firm and golden brown.

